Abdomen. Pruinescence white, dense; dorsal and lateral setae white to silver, often grading into gold. Tergites 2–5 with short anteromedial brown band.
Terminalia
. Dark yellow, pruinescence gray. Tergite 8 (
Fig. 18
), setae white, absent medially on posterior margin. Sternite 8 (
Fig. 20
), anterior margin expanded laterally, sides tapered posteriorly; setae pale yellow. Epandrium (
Fig. 18
